{"tid":1558352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"David Webb (股壇長毛）：831太子站片段不屬私隱條例的個人資料，應公開片段","createTime":"2019-09-10T12:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T05:34:38.000Z","uid":226548,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e80008bbcac8e99360fd91bd20cf0c4da9a18ab7","tid":1558352,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:15:13.000Z","msg":"有股壇長毛之稱的獨立股評人David Webb今日發文稱，港鐵（0066）車務營運總監黃琨暐今日指出，由於要在公眾關注及乘客私穩之間取得平衡，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不能公開8月31日港鐵太子站的閉路電視片段，這是對《個人資料(私隱)條例》（PDPO）的基本誤解。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb認為，這是一個常識，例如是一個人在街上或會認出一個朋友，或會拍攝朋友的相片，或是他在電視上認出一個朋友，但不代表出版商發布了個人資料，因為相片沒有向觀眾披露他是任何人。另一方面，如果觀眾重新發布相片，再加上識別人物的說明，該名觀眾就發布了他們的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Webb認為，公開片段才符合公眾知情權，即使警方及港鐵有任何考慮，亦<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不應以「私穩」的藉口不公開片段</span></strong>。他呼籲，警方及港鐵應該公開所有片段，醜陋謠言（ugly rumours）或可以被真正發生的事實所取代。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果是美國，傳媒可根據信息自由法（Freedom of Information Act）取得警察隨身攝影機及車站閉路電視片段，但香港仍缺乏該法例。他續稱，相關法例的諮詢於今年</span></strong>3月5日結束，至今未有結果，如果香港有以上的法例，就應該應用在法定機構和公眾交通機構。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵今日收市報46.05元，跌0.65%，成交金額2.68億元。"},{"pid":"2e5134fc1ae825d0c4ecf182f344e3f49f3f97bc","tid":1558352,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568106512422&amp;issue=20190910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568106512422%26issue%3D20190910&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4YGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=48fb6e43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568106512422%26issue%3D20190910&h=43438156\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568106512422&amp;issue=20190910</a>"},{"pid":"7dc3dd606e5b8858850e89b12b86b177df184fdd","tid":1558352,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87xSVGP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87xSVGP.jpg&h=2ffe2205&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fd54a73344a6bfa1da7cb71c2d373236be7f9ff","tid":1558352,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kws32nd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKws32nd.jpg&h=d2e2da73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1e3e6a25cef8c4e86f1b5577f28eb362257ef7","tid":1558352,"uid":61191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山人assemble<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRoaoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRoaoS</a>"},{"pid":"67e8db7c64f45fd0a3be7e0391eb6a0477780ebc","tid":1558352,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTNzpAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTNzpAR.jpg&h=49a9881f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6008161596ff6d157533a2bec7b1f56db897ebff","tid":1558352,"uid":54900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d04a06376ab06a0e6e2764af38a2d4f716824e1","tid":1558352,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:35.000Z","msg":"肯定有不可告人的秘密啦！無做錯怕咩公開。"},{"pid":"5cbbb390aa2ad0a7ef44ec3973543fc66aeb99bc","tid":1558352,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b91937ec58ea830b3e1d8070411ca277ee1aaa73","tid":1558352,"uid":132931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"股壇長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f35d5b58f1e7ac92cb3ea98a870ccc1d0a815d","tid":1558352,"uid":60563,"